NSLOCTEXT("435C60C24979BECC972F64A03F0D22D3 [A3D89F074F18F3D1E03A4AA9B995AE63]", "_MyTempName_SubtitleMessage", "Clean the dungeon, and feed the creatures. If you succeed three nights, you will be allowed to enter the next dungeon. You have 6 hours to finish.")
